"``Cache-Control`` 和 ``Location`` 之类的响应头通过 :meth:`Response.set_header` "
"来定义。这个方法接受两个参数，一个是响应头的名字，一个是它的值，名字是大小写敏感的。"

# f0fe9d7d598146ff9d7f6b609556afbb
#: ../../tutorial.rst:392
msgid ""
"Most headers are unique, meaning that only one header per name is send to "
